headline: Strength Seen in Baker Hughes (BKR): Can Its 10.7% Jump Turn into More Strength?
summary: Baker Hughes (BKR) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
